Your item's price may decrease for one of the following reasons:
Base commission — our bot items cost 7% more than user items; Trade lock markup — items with trade lock have an additional commission depending on the number of lock days (from 0 to 13%);
Commission on items that just came out of trade lock — items that just came out of Steam trade lock also have an additional commission. It is fully removed 6 days after unlocking.
